Vital Point to Capture?(23)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to play\b0 .
\par Black played the attacment at 1 and White descended at 2. It was a mistake.
\par
\par Instead of playing at 2, White could easily live with A.
\par
\par Actually Black 1 was also a mistake. Also think about how Black should play from the beginning.
\par
\par }
