Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \cf1\b The opponen's vital point is my vital point.
\par \cf0\b0 Black 1 is the \cf1\b vital point\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par If White connects at 2, Black cuts with 3 and White is dead.
\par If White plays at 3 instead of 2, Black plays at 2 and White is dead again.
\par }
