Dia. 02 White's Hope
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \cf1\b White hopes\cf0\b0  that Black plays at 1 then White 2 becomes a good move.
\par After Black 3 White 4 is sente.
\par
\par White lives with two eyes up to 6.
\par
\par This proves Black 1 was not good.
\par }
