Dia. 03 Black 1, Mistake
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par After Black 1, Black is expecting White to answer at A. It was a \cf1\b mistake\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par However White is not going to block directly. White can live with many points by playing at 2.
\par
\par }
