Dia. 04 Black's Correct Move
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par What was Black's correct move then?
\par The attachment at 1 was right.
\par After White 2, Black can capture White with 3.
\par Black can also play diagonal move at A instead of 3.
\par
\par }
